column5: Solutions are relatively simple....lasting solutions take a little longer.  Thanks.
Don't forget to stop and have lunch eh. It helps to take a break.

I didn't use the backdoor to rat out to TJ this time even tho I noticed it first thing this morning and still down when I got back around 11:30.  My Yahoo emails have been acting up along with a couple other sites I visit. Methinks theres a conspiracy at work somewhere (tongue in cheek) or maybe there's whole bunch of upgrading going on around the interweb. Keep at it Roy, it's a thankless job at times I know!  Michael
C'mon Roy...Admit it...TJ paid the light bill but the cheque bounced...!
My left eye is twitchin, my right foots shakin and never mind the rest..
This is getting bad. Three mornings where I've run out of a way to avoid the Mrs.
who forgot to feed the hamsters?
Go grow something Bruce! I'm leavings 10 minutes earlier for work!  Must be a bit.ch for Lew,  nothing to do! Hei Lew go get us some Christmas meat!
